### Discussion Forum App project made by Sydygaliev Kumar for a project review on Intro to Programming Course on 10.05.2025.

This app was written using Flask framework on Python and SQLAlchemy.

# To run on a local machine:
1. Head to the main directory - `Discussion-Forum-Web-App\`
3. Create a virtual environment - `python -m venv venv` (This step requires Python to be installed)
4. Activate the virtual environment - `.\venv\Scripts\activate` (Windows), `source venv/bin/activate` (Linux/MacOS)
5. Run the command `pip install -r requirements.txt` (If does not work - try `pip install -r .\requirements.txt`)
6. Enter `cd app`
7. Run project using - `flask run`
8. Enter the main page on a browser - `localhost:5000`

# To stop the running app:
1. Press `Ctrl + C`
2. Enter deactivate or close the terminal
